Brunch lovers, you need to check out Sequoia in Raja Park, Jaipur! 🌿✨ 

This spot has the perfect blend of aesthetic interiors, cozy vibes, and absolutely delicious food.

Here’s what we tried (and highly recommend!):

🍕 Farmhouse Pizza 
🥟 Chili Cheese Cream Garlic Dimsum 
🥤 Coffee Shake & Blue Lagoon 
🥐 Chocolate Croissant Bowl 

If you’re looking for a brunch spot with a great vibe, amazing food, and Insta-worthy aesthetics, Sequoia is a must-visit! 💙✨

📍 Raja Park, Jaipur
